<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
        background-color: #fbf9f5; /* brand-cream */
        color: #1e1b18; /* brand-dark */
        margin: 0;
        padding: 20px;
      }
      .wrapper {
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        background: #ffffff;
        border: 1px solid #dfd5c6; /* brand-tan */
        border-radius: 6px;
        overflow: hidden;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
      }
      .header {
        background-color: #1e1b18; /* brand-dark */
        padding: 35px 30px;
        text-align: center;
      }
      .header h1 {
        color: #fbf9f5;
        margin: 0;
        font-size: 26px;
        letter-spacing: 1px;
        font-weight: 700;
      }
      .content {
        padding: 40px 30px;
        line-height: 1.6;
        font-size: 15px;
      }
      .content p {
        margin: 0 0 20px 0;
        color: #1e1b18;
      }
      .highlight-box {
        background-color: #fbf9f5;
        border-left: 4px solid #5f6b5e; /* brand-sage */
        padding: 20px;
        margin: 25px 0;
        border-radius: 0 4px 4px 0;
      }
      .highlight-box h3 {
        margin: 0 0 8px 0;
        color: #a65b32; /* brand-clay */
        font-size: 16px;
      }
      .highlight-box p {
        margin: 0;
        font-size: 14px;
        color: #5f6b5e;
      }
      .signature {
        margin-top: 30px;
        font-weight: 600;
        color: #1e1b18;
      }
      .footer {
        background-color: #dfd5c6; /* brand-tan */
        padding: 20px;
        text-align: center;
        font-size: 11px;
        color: #5f6b5e;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="wrapper">
      <div class="header">
        <h1>DD Cattle Company</h1>
      </div>

      <div class="content">
        <p>Hello <%= @name %>,</p>

        <p>Thank you for reaching out to DD Cattle Company. We wanted to drop you a quick note to let you know that we have successfully received your inquiry sent through our website contact form.</p>

        <div class="highlight-box">
          <h3>What Happens Next?</h3>
          <p>Our team reviews all inquiries individually. Whether you are asking about our Mustang training programs, current horse strings for sale, or custom cattle operations, we make it a priority to get back to you with an honest, thorough answer within 24 to 48 business hours.</p>
        </div>

        <p>If your request is urgent, feel free to reply directly to this email to add any additional context or details.</p>

        <p>We appreciate your interest in our program and look forward to speaking with you soon.</p>

        <div class="signature">
          The DD Cattle Co. Team
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="footer">
        &copy; 2026 DD Cattle Company. All rights reserved.<br>
        North Georgia's premier destination for Mustang training.
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>